        Film: Bad Seeds        </a></h3>
        <p class="small">
        Jacques Thériault, an actor with big gambling debts, takes refuge in the country where he is found by Simon, a sly, uncouth farmer. The men end up becoming friends and begin to grow cannabis. They meet a young Hydro-Québec employee who embraces their project. During the winter harvest, they learn to live together with a degree of happiness. Yet a threat from the outside comes to disturb this delicate balance.
Drama, Comedy</p>
    </div>

</div>
 
