    <div class="col-sm-10 event-main">
       <h3> <a href="https://www.google.com/calendar/event?eid=OWljOGkzZ3FrbDcxYXB1dWZqZjhxY2NscjQgZm9ydGVyaWVwbEBt&ctz=America/Toronto">
 
        Friends of the Library meeting        </a></h3>
        <p class="small">
        Come join the Friends of the Library at 4 p.m. at the Centennial Branch. The Friends are a welcoming, congenial group of library supporters, and will be glad to see you. On the agenda are reports of summer activities promoting the library in the community, and plans for participation in the October 1 How-To Festival. The Friends meet monthly from September to June, raising funds for special library projects. You can email the Friends:  friends@fepl.ca
</p>
